
<p>I&rsquo;ve been putting in some time on side projects every morning while building up the motivation to work on more overwhelming things. Recently the focus was on <a href="https://brettterpstra.com/projects/reiki">Reiki</a>, my tool for running Rake tasks with fuzzy matching and humane argument parsing.</p>

